  <h4><a href="http://www.naifa.org/about-naifa/diversity-inclusion">Diversity & Inclusion</a></h4>
  <p>Advancing diversity and inclusion in the insurance and financial services industry is at the forefront of NAIFA&rsquo;s vision for the future. The Diversity and Inclusion initiative supports NAIFA&#39;s goal to empower members by broadening diversity, bolstering advocacy, developing top-notch training programs and increasing public awareness.<br />
<br />
NAIFA seeks to create a more diverse population of agents who are better equipped to serve a diverse population. Inclusion enhances an organization&rsquo;s ability to achieve better business results by engaging people from diverse backgrounds and perspectives. That is the overall goal of the Diversity Task Force.
